{{Top|leg}}
An '''anti-register''' was a highly illegal device which reversed the action of a [[transfer register]]. Transfer registers recorded transactions throughout the galaxy, by the use of an electro-optical device, which recorded the prints of buyers and sellers. Instead of inputting the required print into a transfer register, an anti-register duplicated the requested print contained within any security or registration system. [[Paxxi Derida]] invented the anti-register, which proved invaluable in the [[Phindian/Legends|Phindian's]] rebellion against the [[Syndicat]]. During the rebellion, Paxxi's anti-register was destroyed by [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] fire when he threw it to protect [[Kaadi]].

